Endometriosis imitating bladder tumor in 2nd trimester of pregnancy. Case presentation of bladder endometriosis during 2nd trimester imitating urinary bladder tumour.Mother and Child Care Institute, Prague. III. Medical School of Charles University, Prague.25-years old patient, 2nd trimester of first pregnancy.Partial bladder cystectomy.Complete recovery succeded by term delivery.Tumouriform endometriosis of urinary bladder successfully treated by partial cystectomy allowing normal term delivery.